---
title: "_setAssetOutReceiver (BaseAuction)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_live: _whenNoLiveAuctions()
    q_check_live --> q_revert_live: live auction exists
    q_revert_live --> [*]: revert LiveAuction
    q_check_live --> q_check_zero: no live auctions
    q_check_zero --> q_revert_zero: assetOutReceiver == address(0)
    q_revert_zero --> [*]: revert InvalidZeroAddress
    q_check_zero --> q_check_same: assetOutReceiver != address(0)
    q_check_same --> q_revert_same: current == assetOutReceiver
    q_revert_same --> [*]: revert ValueNotUpdated
    q_check_same --> q_update: current != assetOutReceiver
    q_update --> [*]: s_assetOutReceiver = assetOutReceiver, emit AssetOutReceiverSet

    note right of q_check_live
        INV-001: No configuration changes during live auctions
        INV-002: assetOutReceiver must be non-zero
    end note
